---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Harkirat Seehra — Harkhy · حركي.">
  <article>
    <p class="category-tag">ABOUT</p>
    <h1>Who Am I?</h1>

    <p>
      My name is <strong>Harkirat Seehra</strong>. This is <strong>THE TRUTH · حقیقت</strong> — I write many things, on many topics. I write what I like.
      I do not follow trends to make a bank in the writing space — writing is about making a mark, making
      a point to elaborate what is in your mind.
    </p>

    <p>
      Professionally, I describe my work as the art of behavioral psychology — because behaviours are the
      outcome of habits. I write psychology of patterns and behaviours which make human beings act in certain
      ways, influenced by their philosophies to live life.
    </p>

    <p>
      The Truth is a spiritual guide for people who are spiritually connected with God regardless of any
      religion. God is one, but every human being feels it differently — like the breath of Jesus, the song
      of Solomon, the music of Mohammad, and the Truth of Guru Nanak.
    </p>

    <p>
      I also write stories — parables, prophetic retellings, and original fiction. Multilingual, unfiltered,
      original.
    </p>

    <p class="contact-line">
      Letters are welcome at <a href="/correspondence">[correspondence]</a>.
      Reply may be slow — the writing comes first.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.category-tag {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: var(--t-xs);
  color: var(--ink-dim);
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

h1 {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: var(--t-2xl);
  color: var(--ink-bright);
  line-height: var(--leading-tight);
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

article p {
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  color: var(--ink);
}

.contact-line {
  margin-top: 2rem;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: var(--t-sm);
  color: var(--ink-dim);
}
</style>
